{"tid":1383273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線中國組]香港反修例的內地民眾視角","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:07:26.000Z","uid":267658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f29e76c1c635bbdd6a9a73482fa5fd925c91b90b","tid":1383273,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/856265858071988/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F856265858071988%2F&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=84eee06d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/856265858071988/</a> <br />\n<br />\n【香港反修例的內地民眾視角】 <br />\n<br />\n香港修例風波，由六月到現在已經一個多月，不少國際媒體都有大篇幅報道，內地民眾對這場運動有多少認識，又有甚麼看法呢? <br />\n<br />\n有人一提起就直斥有份參與的大學生為「暴徒」，又有人直指示威者「很野蠻」。 <br />\n<br />\n如果想在內地看到香港的情況，又可以看到些甚麼?剩下來民眾可以看到的就只有官方報道，和網上流傳的片段，好像一條機場集會圍堵老人家的片，近日就在抖音和不同微信群傳來傳去。 <br />\n<br />\n而在微信上，都有部分自媒體關注香港情況，他們形容香港是暴亂，是港獨分子在禍亂香港，甚至讚揚元朗白衣人打得好，更有人在微博上，發起要去香港保衛元朗。 <br />\n<br />\n但另一邊廂，有內地維權人士就因為在Facebook和Twitter，轉發香港情況，並寫上形勢大好和加油的字眼，而被指尋釁滋事，被行政拘留15日。"},{"pid":"b2ee50214cf802dbdac971c6394ee504e85c5c1f","tid":1383273,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=6ea95973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"},{"pid":"a2c9a8cb0babe2fcb990e1254f3a237ffd3ec579","tid":1383273,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"中國人真係好撚on9"},{"pid":"f59eef8ff48c71e75c3e5485ab11450bda6ddce3","tid":1383273,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e05f06749167b2f45ef0bc40e3aade37695eca9","tid":1383273,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"你同一隻狗講自由民主，佢點會識？<br />\n人話都要搵人先聽得明。"},{"pid":"676282d87a3890ba10f822b3ad1b5fb47e234ce6","tid":1383273,"uid":164374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"班太監話扑野好唔健康,好嘔心喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f7535559058b0e786a5052973a9be5f684e25d","tid":1383273,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"愚民政策，有啲知情但驚事，有啲真喺信內地媒體所報導"},{"pid":"211498d2944bb8074c9355fb51abaace49d3f5eb","tid":1383273,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f7535559058b0e786a5052973a9be5f684e25d","tid":1383273,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"愚民政策，有啲知情但驚事，有啲真喺信內地媒體所報導"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"ed74df510606e4d7c248a85833948343cb986f4d","tid":1383273,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"實有方法反中共洗腦<br />\n我建議大家去同清醒大陸網友交流（例如新品蔥）"},{"pid":"b90f307c577491a29b91a2c9409528fe4b1a7fbe","tid":1383273,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br /